    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473300/extras/TitleLogo.png?t=1755305891\" /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>📖Free-Placement Tower Defense × Roguelike</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473300/extras/30a814fd5dd4163aa808e33c23a8d82f.poster.avif?t=1755305891\" width=660 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473300/extras/30a814fd5dd4163aa808e33c23a8d82f.webm?t=1755305891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a free-placement tower defense game where there are no fixed enemy paths, allowing you to place units anywhere.<br>The placement of your units can influence the routes enemies take. Some enemies will attack you, adding enjoyment as you strategize while considering their unique traits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473300/extras/CardChoice.gif?t=1755305891\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During battles, you’ll face numerous choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What might be inside the treasure chests you open?👀</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>📖Give jobs to your cute companions and take command of the battlefield!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473300/extras/JobChenge.gif?t=1755305891\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The 【Novices】 will fight hard even as they are,<br>but assigning them jobs will make them even more effective.<br>Level them up, and they’ll gain job-specific skills to shine even brighter.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
